data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the perfect location!  This stunning 3-bedroom 2-bathroom and a den/office has been maintained and is ready for you to move in.   This home has beautiful features: brand new roof, tiles throughout the all house, gorgeous kitchen with upgraded cabinets, granite countertop, stainless-steel appliances!  and renovated both bathrooms.  The main bedroom and bath have huge space with breathtaking view of the pool. White metal Dura fence, back porch, inground pool, decorative concrete deck and screen enclosed. Gutters around the house. Close to Win Dixie Plaza and shopping center, Bank and schools. This home won't disappoint you!
